            "type": "text",
            "text": "The Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign voice API enables seamless integration of the Qwen3_TTS_12Hz_1_7B_VoiceDesign model into applications, offering customizable voice synthesis with low latency. This guide provides actionable steps for API teams to deploy and manage this service in production."
          }
